title: Ep. 49: Why You Should Buy Commodities Today
itunes:title: Why You Should Buy Commodities Today
description: Byron King, editor of Outstanding Investments newsletter, sees gold prices over $2,000 an ounce. Resource Report editor Matt Badiali is bullish on natural gas and jr. gold miners. Frank gives his analysis on GS, C, FLR, AAPL, GOOG after earnings.
